long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Once installed, the Login-cat new tab welcomes you with a start page containing wallpapers with photos of beautiful cats and a search bar.  

What do you get with the Login-cat extension?

Cat themes: Enjoy a wide range of adorable cat-themed wallpapers, and discover more cat wallpapers everyday

Speed dials for quicker access: Manage your favorite sites and get quicker access and login to the sites you frequently browse. 

Customized Speed dials: Pin additional sites to customize your new tab.

By clicking “Add to Chrome,” I accept and agree to install Login-cat extension and set the New Tab to www.login-cat.com as provided by the service under the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. 

Terms of use: http://info.login-cat.com/Terms-cs
Privacy policy:http://info.login-cat.com/legal-privacy-cs"
